## 10. Conclusion

QuantumChain rethinks L1 design for the mobile, post-quantum era. By using phones for useful 
work and PQC for signatures, we aim to democratize consensus without sacrificing security.

This is v2.0 of a living document. It will evolve as research completes. 
The next document is THREAT_MODEL.md v1.0.

**Build in public. Audit everything. Launch when safe.**

